        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "> I would rather prevent the buffer from unloading unexpectedly here as done in #21921, which was later reverted🤔 Or otherwise try to figure out why the extmark is still valid but the text isn't there anymore.\r\n\r\n@luukvbaal That makes sense. Both my fix and the patch you mentioned in #39055 only mask the error after the buffer has been unloaded unexpectedly. I'll try to fix it at the source by preventing the msg buffer from being unloaded on tabpage close (the #21921 direction) ",
